    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Python-的数据结构-List-Tuple-Dict-Set"><a href="#Python-的数据结构-List-Tuple-Dict-Set" class="headerlink" title="Python 的数据结构 List Tuple Dict Set"></a>Python 的数据结构 List Tuple Dict Set</h2><h4 id="两个辅助函数让你学习更轻松-help-查看方法的使用方式-dir-查看类的子方法"><a href="#两个辅助函数让你学习更轻松-help-查看方法的使用方式-dir-查看类的子方法" class="headerlink" title="两个辅助函数让你学习更轻松 help (查看方法的使用方式) dir(查看类的子方法)"></a>两个辅助函数让你学习更轻松 help (查看方法的使用方式) dir(查看类的子方法)</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = <span class="string">"life is short use Python"</span></span><br><span class="line">print(dir(a))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>[&apos;__add__&apos;, &apos;__class__&apos;, &apos;__contains__&apos;, &apos;__delattr__&apos;, &apos;__dir__&apos;, &apos;__doc__&apos;, &apos;__eq__&apos;, &apos;__format__&apos;, &apos;__ge__&apos;, &apos;__getattribute__&apos;, &apos;__getitem__&apos;, &apos;__getnewargs__&apos;, &apos;__gt__&apos;, &apos;__hash__&apos;, &apos;__init__&apos;, &apos;__init_subclass__&apos;, &apos;__iter__&apos;, &apos;__le__&apos;, &apos;__len__&apos;, &apos;__lt__&apos;, &apos;__mod__&apos;, &apos;__mul__&apos;, &apos;__ne__&apos;, &apos;__new__&apos;, &apos;__reduce__&apos;, &apos;__reduce_ex__&apos;, &apos;__repr__&apos;, &apos;__rmod__&apos;, &apos;__rmul__&apos;, &apos;__setattr__&apos;, &apos;__sizeof__&apos;, &apos;__str__&apos;, &apos;__subclasshook__&apos;, &apos;capitalize&apos;, &apos;casefold&apos;, &apos;center&apos;, &apos;count&apos;, &apos;encode&apos;, &apos;endswith&apos;, &apos;expandtabs&apos;, &apos;find&apos;, &apos;format&apos;, &apos;format_map&apos;, &apos;index&apos;, &apos;isalnum&apos;, &apos;isalpha&apos;, &apos;isascii&apos;, &apos;isdecimal&apos;, &apos;isdigit&apos;, &apos;isidentifier&apos;, &apos;islower&apos;, &apos;isnumeric&apos;, &apos;isprintable&apos;, &apos;isspace&apos;, &apos;istitle&apos;, &apos;isupper&apos;, &apos;join&apos;, &apos;ljust&apos;, &apos;lower&apos;, &apos;lstrip&apos;, &apos;maketrans&apos;, &apos;partition&apos;, &apos;replace&apos;, &apos;rfind&apos;, &apos;rindex&apos;, &apos;rjust&apos;, &apos;rpartition&apos;, &apos;rsplit&apos;, &apos;rstrip&apos;, &apos;split&apos;, &apos;splitlines&apos;, &apos;startswith&apos;, &apos;strip&apos;, &apos;swapcase&apos;, &apos;title&apos;, &apos;translate&apos;, &apos;upper&apos;, &apos;zfill&apos;]</code></pre><a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">help(a.strip)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>Help on built-in function strip:strip(chars=None, /) method of builtins.str instance    Return a copy of the string with leading and trailing whitespace remove.    If chars is given and not None, remove characters in chars instead.</code></pre><h4 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h4><p>list 是一种有序的集合，可以随时添加和删除其中的元素<br>list 是一个可变的有序表</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros = [<span class="string">'iron man'</span>, <span class="string">'spider man'</span>, <span class="string">'egg man'</span>]</span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">f'<span class="subst">&#123;heros&#125;</span> \n type: <span class="subst">&#123;type(heros)&#125;</span>'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>[&apos;iron man&apos;, &apos;spider man&apos;, &apos;egg man&apos;] type: &lt;class &apos;list&apos;&gt;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">len(heros)  <span class="comment">#  获取列表的长度</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>3</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros[<span class="number">0</span>]  <span class="comment"># 角标从0开始 默认是长度-1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>&apos;iron man&apos;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros[<span class="number">1</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>&apos;spider man&apos;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros[<span class="number">3</span>]  <span class="comment"># 超出索引</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>---------------------------------------------------------------------------IndexError                                Traceback (most recent call last)&lt;ipython-input-75-8dc1ea78ff1c&gt; in &lt;module&gt;----&gt; 1 heros[3]  # 超出索引IndexError: list index out of range</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros[<span class="number">-1</span>] <span class="comment"># 从后往前取值</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>&apos;egg man&apos;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros.insert(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="string">'wo man'</span>)  <span class="comment"># 指定索引插入</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>[&apos;iron man&apos;, &apos;spider man&apos;, &apos;egg man&apos;, &apos;wo man&apos;]</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros[<span class="number">3</span>] = <span class="string">'woo man'</span>  <span class="comment"># 更新元素</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>[&apos;iron man&apos;, &apos;spider man&apos;, &apos;egg man&apos;, &apos;woo man&apos;]</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros.pop()  <span class="comment">#  弹出最后一个元素并返回</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>&apos;woo man&apos;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>[&apos;iron man&apos;, &apos;spider man&apos;, &apos;egg man&apos;]</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros.pop(<span class="number">1</span>)  <span class="comment"># 指定索弹出元素</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>&apos;spider man&apos;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>[&apos;iron man&apos;, &apos;egg man&apos;]</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros.append(<span class="string">'add man'</span>)  <span class="comment"># 追加元素到列表</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">heros</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>[&apos;iron man&apos;, &apos;egg man&apos;, &apos;add man&apos;]</code></pre><h4 id="元组"><a href="#元组" class="headerlink" title="元组"></a>元组</h4><p>tuple 和 list 非常类似，但是 tuple 一旦初始化就不能修改</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">t = ()</span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">f"<span class="subst">&#123;t&#125;</span> \n <span class="subst">&#123;type(t)&#125;</span>"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>() &lt;class &apos;tuple&apos;&gt;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">t = (<span class="number">2</span>) <span class="comment"># (2)一个元素时 不能这样定义</span></span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">f"<span class="subst">&#123;t&#125;</span> \n <span class="subst">&#123;type(t)&#125;</span>"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>2 &lt;class &apos;int&apos;&gt;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tt = (<span class="number">2</span>,)  <span class="comment"># 只有1个元素的tuple时，也会加一个逗号,</span></span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">f"<span class="subst">&#123;tt&#125;</span> \n <span class="subst">&#123;type(tt)&#125;</span>"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>(2,) &lt;class &apos;tuple&apos;&gt;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">print(dir(tt))  <span class="comment"># 元组的属性</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>[&apos;__add__&apos;, &apos;__class__&apos;, &apos;__contains__&apos;, &apos;__delattr__&apos;, &apos;__dir__&apos;, &apos;__doc__&apos;, &apos;__eq__&apos;, &apos;__format__&apos;, &apos;__ge__&apos;, &apos;__getattribute__&apos;, &apos;__getitem__&apos;, &apos;__getnewargs__&apos;, &apos;__gt__&apos;, &apos;__hash__&apos;, &apos;__init__&apos;, &apos;__init_subclass__&apos;, &apos;__iter__&apos;, &apos;__le__&apos;, &apos;__len__&apos;, &apos;__lt__&apos;, &apos;__mul__&apos;, &apos;__ne__&apos;, &apos;__new__&apos;, &apos;__reduce__&apos;, &apos;__reduce_ex__&apos;, &apos;__repr__&apos;, &apos;__rmul__&apos;, &apos;__setattr__&apos;, &apos;__sizeof__&apos;, &apos;__str__&apos;, &apos;__subclasshook__&apos;, &apos;count&apos;, &apos;index&apos;]</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">demo = (<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,[<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">8</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">demo[<span class="number">2</span>][<span class="number">0</span>] = <span class="number">100</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">demo  <span class="comment"># 此时tuple内元素变了 那可以说 tuple为可变序列吗?</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>(1, 2, [100, 8])</code></pre><h4 id="字典"><a href="#字典" class="headerlink" title="字典"></a>字典</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">kw = &#123;<span class="string">"name"</span>: <span class="string">"test"</span>, <span class="string">"age"</span>: <span class="number">12</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">f"<span class="subst">&#123;kw&#125;</span> \n <span class="subst">&#123;type(kw)&#125;</span>"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>{&apos;name&apos;: &apos;test&apos;, &apos;age&apos;: 12} &lt;class &apos;dict&apos;&gt;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">kw[<span class="string">'name'</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>&apos;test&apos;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">kw[<span class="string">'name1'</span>]  <span class="comment"># key找不到空报错</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>---------------------------------------------------------------------------KeyError                                  Traceback (most recent call last)&lt;ipython-input-96-69178caa756c&gt; in &lt;module&gt;----&gt; 1 kw[&apos;name1&apos;]  # key找不到空报错KeyError: &apos;name1&apos;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">kw.get(<span class="string">'name1'</span>, <span class="literal">None</span>)    <span class="comment"># key找不到, 返回None</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">kw[<span class="string">'sex'</span>] = <span class="string">'man'</span>  <span class="comment"># 增加字段</span></span><br><span class="line">kw</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>{&apos;name&apos;: &apos;test&apos;, &apos;age&apos;: 12, &apos;sex&apos;: &apos;man&apos;}</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">kw.pop(<span class="string">'age'</span>)  <span class="comment"># 删除字段</span></span><br><span class="line">kw</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>{&apos;name&apos;: &apos;test&apos;, &apos;sex&apos;: &apos;man&apos;}</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">print(dir(kw))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>[&apos;__class__&apos;, &apos;__contains__&apos;, &apos;__delattr__&apos;, &apos;__delitem__&apos;, &apos;__dir__&apos;, &apos;__doc__&apos;, &apos;__eq__&apos;, &apos;__format__&apos;, &apos;__ge__&apos;, &apos;__getattribute__&apos;, &apos;__getitem__&apos;, &apos;__gt__&apos;, &apos;__hash__&apos;, &apos;__init__&apos;, &apos;__init_subclass__&apos;, &apos;__iter__&apos;, &apos;__le__&apos;, &apos;__len__&apos;, &apos;__lt__&apos;, &apos;__ne__&apos;, &apos;__new__&apos;, &apos;__reduce__&apos;, &apos;__reduce_ex__&apos;, &apos;__repr__&apos;, &apos;__setattr__&apos;, &apos;__setitem__&apos;, &apos;__sizeof__&apos;, &apos;__str__&apos;, &apos;__subclasshook__&apos;, &apos;clear&apos;, &apos;copy&apos;, &apos;fromkeys&apos;, &apos;get&apos;, &apos;items&apos;, &apos;keys&apos;, &apos;pop&apos;, &apos;popitem&apos;, &apos;setdefault&apos;, &apos;update&apos;, &apos;values&apos;]</code></pre><p>set 和 dict 类似，也是一组 key 的集合，但不存储 value。由于 key 不能重复，所以，在 set 中，没有重复的 key</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s = set([<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">4</span>])</span><br><span class="line">s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>{1, 2, 3, 4}</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s.add(<span class="number">4</span>)  <span class="comment"># 增加 元素中有的 不添加</span></span><br><span class="line">s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>{1, 2, 3, 4}</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s.add(<span class="number">33</span>)</span><br><span class="line">s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>{1, 2, 3, 4, 33}</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s.remove(<span class="number">2</span>) <span class="comment"># 删除key</span></span><br><span class="line">s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>{1, 3, 4, 33}</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ss = set([<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">4</span>])  <span class="comment"># 数学交集</span></span><br><span class="line">s&amp;ss</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>{3, 4}</code></pre>]]></content>
    
