  <entry>
    <title>Python 基础学习 之 数据类型</title>
    <link href="http://blog.ealine.cn/2019/09/23/python-base-value/"/>
    <id>http://blog.ealine.cn/2019/09/23/python-base-value/</id>
    <published>2019-09-23T11:25:06.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-09-23T11:28:17.500Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="变量命名规则：-变量名必须是大小写英文、数字和-的组合，且不能用数字开头"><a href="#变量命名规则：-变量名必须是大小写英文、数字和-的组合，且不能用数字开头" class="headerlink" title="变量命名规则： 变量名必须是大小写英文、数字和_的组合，且不能用数字开头"></a>变量命名规则： 变量名必须是大小写英文、数字和_的组合，且不能用数字开头</h3><h4 id="整形变量"><a href="#整形变量" class="headerlink" title="整形变量"></a>整形变量</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">print(<span class="string">"Python可以处理任意大小的整数，当然包括负整数，在程序中的表示方法和数学上的写法一模一样"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">a = <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">f"a: <span class="subst">&#123;a&#125;</span> ; type: <span class="subst">&#123;type(a)&#125;</span>"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>Python可以处理任意大小的整数，当然包括负整数，在程序中的表示方法和数学上的写法一模一样a: 1 ; type: &lt;class &apos;int&apos;&gt;</code></pre><a id="more"></a><h4 id="浮点形变量"><a href="#浮点形变量" class="headerlink" title="浮点形变量"></a>浮点形变量</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">b = <span class="number">3.14</span></span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">f"b: <span class="subst">&#123;b&#125;</span> ; type: <span class="subst">&#123;type(b)&#125;</span>"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>b: 3.14 ; type: &lt;class &apos;float&apos;&gt;</code></pre><h4 id="布尔形变量"><a href="#布尔形变量" class="headerlink" title="布尔形变量"></a>布尔形变量</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">d = <span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">f"d: <span class="subst">&#123;d&#125;</span> ; type: <span class="subst">&#123;type(d)&#125;</span>"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>d: True ; type: &lt;class &apos;bool&apos;&gt;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">not</span> d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>False</code></pre><h4 id="空值"><a href="#空值" class="headerlink" title="空值"></a>空值</h4><p>空值是 Python 里一个特殊的值，用 None 表示。None 不能理解为 0，因为 0 是有意义的，而 None 是一个特殊的空值。</p><h4 id="复数"><a href="#复数" class="headerlink" title="复数"></a>复数</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">aa = <span class="number">12</span><span class="number">-12j</span></span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">f"aa: <span class="subst">&#123;aa&#125;</span> ; type: <span class="subst">&#123;type(aa)&#125;</span>"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">f"real: <span class="subst">&#123;aa.real&#125;</span> ; imag: <span class="subst">&#123;aa.imag&#125;</span>"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>aa: (12-12j) ; type: &lt;class &apos;complex&apos;&gt;real: 12.0 ; imag: -12.0</code></pre><h4 id="字符串变量"><a href="#字符串变量" class="headerlink" title="字符串变量"></a>字符串变量</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">c = <span class="string">"I'm superman"</span></span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">f"c: <span class="subst">&#123;c&#125;</span> ; type: <span class="subst">&#123;type(c)&#125;</span>"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>c: I&apos;m superman ; type: &lt;class &apos;str&apos;&gt;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cc = <span class="string">'I\'m superman'</span></span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">"字符串转译 \\"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">f"cc: <span class="subst">&#123;cc&#125;</span> ; type: <span class="subst">&#123;type(cc)&#125;</span>"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>字符串转译 \cc: I&apos;m superman ; type: &lt;class &apos;str&apos;&gt;</code></pre><p>用于定义字符串<br>单引号字符串：’abc’<br>双引号字符串：”abc”<br>三引号字符串：’’’abc’’’(三单引号),”””abc”””（三双引号）<br>总结：<br>（1）单引号内可以使用双引号，中间的内容会当作字符串打印<br>（2）双引号内可以使用单引号，中间的内容会当作字符串打印<br>（3）三单引号和三双引号中间的字符串在输出时会保持原来的格式。</p><h4 id="字符串与-Unicode-ord-str-gt-unicode-chr-unicode-gt-str"><a href="#字符串与-Unicode-ord-str-gt-unicode-chr-unicode-gt-str" class="headerlink" title="字符串与 Unicode ord (str-&gt;unicode) chr(unicode-&gt;str)"></a>字符串与 Unicode ord (str-&gt;unicode) chr(unicode-&gt;str)</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">str1 = <span class="string">"A"</span></span><br><span class="line">ord(str1)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>65</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">str2 = chr(<span class="number">65</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">str2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>&apos;A&apos;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">'ABC'</span>.encode(<span class="string">'ascii'</span>)   <span class="comment"># 纯英文的str可以用ASCII编码为bytes</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>b&apos;ABC&apos;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">'中文'</span>.encode(<span class="string">'ascii'</span>) <span class="comment"># 中文的bytes超出了ASCII的编码范围</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>---------------------------------------------------------------------------UnicodeEncodeError                        Traceback (most recent call last)&lt;ipython-input-47-c12ead4e1785&gt; in &lt;module&gt;----&gt; 1 &apos;中文&apos;.encode(&apos;ascii&apos;) # 中文的bytes超出了ASCII的编码范围UnicodeEncodeError: &apos;ascii&apos; codec can&apos;t encode characters in position 0-1: ordinal not in range(128)</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">'中文'</span>.encode(<span class="string">'utf-8'</span>)<span class="comment"># 中文的str可以用UTF-8编码为bytes</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>b&apos;\xe4\xb8\xad\xe6\x96\x87&apos;</code></pre><h3 id="字符串与-bytes-encode-str-gt-bytes-decode-bytes-gt-str"><a href="#字符串与-bytes-encode-str-gt-bytes-decode-bytes-gt-str" class="headerlink" title="字符串与 bytes encode (str -&gt; bytes) decode (bytes -&gt; str)"></a>字符串与 bytes encode (str -&gt; bytes) decode (bytes -&gt; str)</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bb = <span class="string">b'ABC'</span></span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">f"bb: <span class="subst">&#123;bb&#125;</span> ; type: <span class="subst">&#123;type(bb)&#125;</span>"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>bb: b&apos;ABC&apos; ; type: &lt;class &apos;bytes&apos;&gt;</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bb1 = <span class="string">b'中文'</span>  <span class="comment"># 中文超出了ASCII范围</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>  File &quot;&lt;ipython-input-50-95fe25c7687e&gt;&quot;, line 1    bb1 = b&apos;中文&apos;  # 中文超出了ASCII范围         ^SyntaxError: bytes can only contain ASCII literal characters.</code></pre><h3 id="字符串拼接-格式化"><a href="#字符串拼接-格式化" class="headerlink" title="字符串拼接|格式化"></a>字符串拼接|格式化</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">print(<span class="string">"字符串拼接"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">name = <span class="string">"test"</span></span><br><span class="line">answer = <span class="string">"i am "</span> + name</span><br><span class="line">print(answer)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>字符串拼接i am test</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">print(<span class="string">"字符串格式化 %"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">name1 = <span class="string">"zhangsan"</span></span><br><span class="line">answer1 = <span class="string">"我是: %s"</span> % name1</span><br><span class="line">print(answer1)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>字符串格式化 %我是: zhangsan</code></pre><p>占位符 替换内容<br>%d 整数<br>%f 浮点数<br>%s 字符串<br>%x 十六进制整数</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">print(<span class="string">'%.2f'</span> % <span class="number">3.1415926</span>)  <span class="comment">#浮点数 保留两位小数</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>3.14</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">print(<span class="string">"字符串格式化 format"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">answer2 = <span class="string">"我是&#123;&#125;, 今天天气&#123;&#125;"</span>.format(<span class="string">'张三'</span>, <span class="string">'很不错'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">print(answer2)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>字符串格式化 format我是张三, 今天天气很不错</code></pre>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h3 id=&quot;变量命名规则：-变量名必须是大小写英文、数字和-的组合，且不能用数字开头&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#变量命名规则：-变量名必须是大小写英文、数字和-的组合，且不能用数字开头&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;变量命名规则： 变量名必须是大小写英文、数字和_的组合，且不能用数字开头&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;变量命名规则： 变量名必须是大小写英文、数字和_的组合，且不能用数字开头&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h4 id=&quot;整形变量&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#整形变量&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;整形变量&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;整形变量&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight python&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;print(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&quot;Python可以处理任意大小的整数，当然包括负整数，在程序中的表示方法和数学上的写法一模一样&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;a = &lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;print(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;f&quot;a: &lt;span class=&quot;subst&quot;&gt;&amp;#123;a&amp;#125;&lt;/span&gt; ; type: &lt;span class=&quot;subst&quot;&gt;&amp;#123;type(a)&amp;#125;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;Python可以处理任意大小的整数，当然包括负整数，在程序中的表示方法和数学上的写法一模一样
